Package: botscan
Type: Package
Title: Scans Twitter Conversations For Bots
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Kurt Wirth
Maintainer: Kurt Wirth <KurtAWirth@gmail.com>
Description: This package accepts any Twitter search query as an input and
    outputs the percentage of users producing that conversation that are
    predicted to be non-human, or "bots". This tool uses rtweets to search
    Twitter and botrnot and its machine learning technique to analyze handles.
    IMPORTANT - In order to install this package, you must first install botrnot 
    from https://github.com/mkearney/botrnot.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    rtweet,
    botrnot
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: testthat
